THANKS TO BANK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 An article on Aug. 1 regarding the Ventura County Symphony Assn.'s recent 
deficit stated that the Discovery Artists concert "lack(ed) a major sponsor." 
Not true.The Bank of A. Levy generously contributed a grant of $10,000 to 
support the concert. That contribution, plus the $4,000 in ticket sales, 
allowed the event to lose only $15,000. Without the bank's support, the concert 
would not have been considered. 
</P>
