 PROPOSITIONS WIN BIG 
</P>
<P>
 Two controversial initiatives have widespread support in Orange County. A 
plurality of self-described liberals and two-thirds of middle-of-the-roaders 
back Proposition 187. Proposition 184 is a huge winner here: 
</P>
<P>
 *** 
</P>
