<P>
 USX to Raise Steel Prices: The nation's largest steelmaker announced 
much-anticipated price hikes for sheet steel, reflecting the strong market 
outlook for steel.USX-U.S. Steel Group said that beginning in January, it will 
raise prices by $30 a ton for all sheet products, as well as on the base price 
of all plate products, including carbon and high-strength low-alloy. Sheet 
steel, by far the largest steel market, is used in automobiles and appliances. 
